				},
				"string" : "For the  [Smalltalk Meetup Zurich](https://zurich.smalltalk.world) on 2026-04-26.\nMost of the examples are from the GT Book page {{gtPage:Playing with LLMs|db=2j9m7db2i4oz116bexd7wbdxo}}.\nThe presentation is loosely based on TG's YouTube video: [\nGT Live: Moldable Chat](https://youtu.be/y0FQrVq74BI?si=KWq0FI1Ib48PWNxo).\nSee the notes in my private db: {{gtPage:Notes from TG's Moldable Chat video|db=cqvjoxfnf6zd764ibqa67pln6}}"
